# These rules set flowbits checked by your other enabled rules.  If the
# dependent flowbits are not set, then some of your chosen rules may
# not fire.  Enabling all rules that set these dependent flowbits ensures
# your chosen rules fire as intended.
#
# If you wish to prevent alerts from any of these rules, add the GID:SID
# of the rule to the Suppression List for the interface.

